I '''Raymond Chen''' metung yang bantug a manalkus kareng [[Microsoft Windows|Windows]] [[Windows Shell|Shell]] koponan king [[Microsoft]]. Manibat mikiabe ya king Microsoft inyang [[1992]], i Chen penigobran ne ing [[OS/2]], [[Windows 95]], [[DirectX]], ampong ding aliwang kasapni na pa ning Windows.  Kilual ning Microsoft, bantug ya keng kayang articulu keng Windows programming.  <ref>{{cite web | url=http://blog.ryjones.org/category/work/microsoft/quotable-raymond/ | title='Quotable Raymond' Category | author=Raymond Chen | work=Mindless Bit Spew | accessdate=2008-11-01 }}</ref> and his custom of wearing suits at work.<ref name=MysticMicrosoft>{{cite web | url=http://www.mysticmicrosoft.com/Chapter16.htm | title=Fade to Light (Chapter 16) | author=Kraig Brockschmidt | work=Mystic Microsoft | accessdate=2006-12-30 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://blogs.msdn.com/oldnewthing/archive/2003/09/11/54888.aspx | title=You too can dress like Raymond | author=Raymond Chen | date=September 11, 2003 | work=The Old New Thing | accessdate=2006-12-30 }}</ref>

